## Rules Summary

- ✅ All global providers in `providers/app/index.tsx`
- ✅ Lazy load Monaco Editor and heavy animations
- ✅ Set `staleTime` explicitly on all queries
- ✅ Use Supabase real-time for live chat updates
- ✅ Toast errors always in Arabic
- ❌ Never `console.log` in committed code
